skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: seaside sounds
des: Imagine youself sitting by the seaside, without a care in the world, listening to the waves wash onshore as you slowly drift to sleep. Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Seaside Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
